data.description: Welcome to an exquisite corner lot home with lots of trees and shrubs. BBQ area on back patio and large deck off kitchen-great for entertaining. High privacy fenced back yard plus cement floored storage shed.   Home has all new paint on exterior. Kitchen and dining area very open and has china hutch that is included. Kitchen has 3 sides of cabinets, refrigerator, sink, dishwasher, micro-wave . Home comes with washer and dryer plus all curtains and rods. Downstairs is a very large family room with  insert,Family room at one time had a wet bar which has been removed, making a large family room.  Back yard has a firepit as well as an area for a hot tub nestled in all the trees and shrubs and enclosed with high privacy fence. Home is on a corner lot which allows extra parking plus the 2 car garage with lots of shelving.
